OL,3,CWhat you need to know on polling day
OL,4,Cin the North East
OL,6,FWhat you need to know
OL,8,FPolling stations will be open from 7am
OL,9,Funtil 10pm on Thursday 7 May.
OL,11,FYou will need an accepted form of
OL,12,Fphoto ID to vote in person.
OL,14,FWhen will we get the results?
OL,16,FIn Hartlepool, results are being
OL,17,Fcounted overnight, and are due to be
OL,18,Fdeclared in the early hours of Friday
OL,19,Fmorning.
