OL,3,CWhat you need to know on polling day
OL,4,Cin the North East
OL,6,FFor all of the other councils in the
OL,7,FNorth East, results are being counted
OL,8,Fduring the daytime on Friday.
OL,10,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,11,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,12,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,13,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,14,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,15,Fbelow...
